subject: Stadiums and Arenas
Football
Prices (Fares, Fees and Rates)
lead_paragraph: The Giants said Thursday that they had sold more than 70,000 personal seat licenses at the 82,500-seat stadium they are building with the Jets. The remaining unsold P.S.L.’s are in the high-priced club areas, where they cost $7,500 to $20,000 each.
